@startuml
title Последовательность обработки пользовательского сообщения

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Times New Roman"

actor "Пользователь" as User
participant "Web / Telegram" as UI
participant "Django API" as API
participant "Chat service" as Chat
participant "Safety router" as Safety
participant "Ollama / Qwen3" as LLM
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

User -> UI : Ввод сообщения
UI -> API : POST /api/v1/chat/messages/
API -> Chat : create_chat_turn()
Chat -> DB : save user message
Chat -> Safety : assess_user_message()
Safety --> Chat : risk_level + route decision

alt low / elevated
    Chat -> LLM : prompt + history + scenario
    LLM --> Chat : generated reply
    Chat -> Safety : apply_response_policy()
else high / critical
    Safety --> Chat : scripted safe response
end

Chat -> DB : save bot message
Chat -> DB : create safety_audit_log
Chat --> API : response payload
API --> UI : JSON
UI --> User : Ответ системы
@enduml
